        <text x="200" y="240" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="20" fill="#FFFFFF">EV Charging Solution</text>
        <text x="200" y="270" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="16" fill="#FFFFFF">Power Conversion with SiC Components</text>
